{"id":885,"parent_id":877,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":885,"title":"Daniel 8","subtitle":"","short_title":"Dan.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 8"],[".studySummary",["i","Daniel sees in vision a ram (Media and Persia), a goat (Greece), four other kings, and then, in the last days, a fierce king who will destroy the holy people—This king will be broken when he stands up against the Prince of Princes."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.1","order":"02.28.008.59569"},["b","1"],"In the third year of the reign of king Belshazzar a vision appeared unto me,",["i","even unto"],"me Daniel, after that which appeared unto me at the first."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.2","order":"02.28.008.59570"},["b","2"],"And I saw in a vision; and it came to pass, when I saw, that I",["i","was"],"at Shushan",["i","in"],"the palace, which",["i","is"],"in the province of Elam; and I saw in a vision, and I was by the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"river"],"of Ulai."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.3","order":"02.28.008.59571"},["b","3"],"Then I lifted up mine eyes, and saw, and, behold, there stood before the river a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"ram"],"which had",["i","two"],"horns: and the",["i","two"],"horns",["i","were"],"high; but one",["i","was"],"higher than the other, and the higher came up last."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.4","order":"02.28.008.59572"},["b","4"],"I saw the ram",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"pushing"],"westward, and northward, and southward; so that no beasts might stand before him, neither",["i","was there any"],"that could deliver out of his hand; but he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"did"],"according to his will, and became great."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.5","order":"02.28.008.59573"},["b","5"],"And as I was considering, behold, an he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"goat"],"came from the west on the face of the whole earth, and touched not the ground: and the goat",["i","had"],"a notable horn between his eyes."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.6","order":"02.28.008.59574"},["b","6"],"And he came to the ram that had",["i","two"],"horns, which I had seen standing before the river, and ran unto him in the fury of his power."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.7","order":"02.28.008.59575"},["b","7"],"And I saw him come close unto the ram, and he was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"moved"],"with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"choler"],"against him, and smote the ram, and brake his two horns: and there was no power in the ram to stand before him, but he cast him down to the ground, and stamped upon him: and there was none that could deliver the ram out of his hand."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.8","order":"02.28.008.59576"},["b","8"],"Therefore the he goat waxed very great: and when he was strong, the great horn was broken; and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"for it"],"came up",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"four"],"notable ones toward the four winds of heaven."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.9","order":"02.28.008.59577"},["b","9"],"And out of one of them came forth a little",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"horn"],", which waxed exceeding great, toward the south, and toward the east, and toward the pleasant",["i","land."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.10","order":"02.28.008.59578"},["b","10"],"And it waxed great,",["i","even"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"to"],"the host of heaven; and it cast down",["i","some"],"of the host and of the stars to the ground, and stamped upon them."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.11","order":"02.28.008.59579"},["b","11"],"Yea, he magnified",["i","himself"],"even to the prince of the host, and by him the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"daily"],["i",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sacrifice"]],"was taken away, and the place of his sanctuary was",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"cast down"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.12","order":"02.28.008.59580"},["b","12"],"And an host was given",["i","him"],"against the daily",["i","sacrifice"],"by reason of transgression, and it cast down the truth to the ground; and it practised, and prospered."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.13","order":"02.28.008.59581"},["b","13"],"¶Then I heard one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"saint"],"speaking, and another saint said unto that certain",["i","saint"],"which spake, How long",["i","shall be"],"the vision",["i","concerning"],"the daily",["i","sacrifice,"],"and the transgression of desolation, to give both the sanctuary and the host to be trodden under foot?"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.14","order":"02.28.008.59582"},["b","14"],"And he said unto me, Unto two thousand and three hundred days; then shall the sanctuary be cleansed."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.15","order":"02.28.008.59583"},["b","15"],"¶And it came to pass, when I,",["i","even"],"I Daniel, had seen the vision, and sought for the meaning, then, behold, there stood before me as the appearance of a man."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.16","order":"02.28.008.59584"},["b","16"],"And I heard a man’s voice between",["i","the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"banks"],"of"],"Ulai, which called, and said,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Gabriel"],", make this",["i","man"],"to understand the vision."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.17","order":"02.28.008.59585"},["b","17"],"So he came near where I stood: and when he came, I was afraid, and fell upon my face: but he said unto me, Understand, O son of man: for at the time of the end",["i","shall be"],"the vision."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.18","order":"02.28.008.59586"},["b","18"],"Now as he was speaking with me, I was in a deep sleep on my face toward the ground: but he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"touched"],"me, and set me upright."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.19","order":"02.28.008.59587"},["b","19"],"And he said, Behold, I will make thee know what shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"in"],"the last end of the indignation: for at the time appointed the end",["i","shall be."]],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.20","order":"02.28.008.59588"},["b","20"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"ram"],"which thou sawest having",["i","two"],"horns",["i","are"],"the kings of Media and Persia."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.21","order":"02.28.008.59589"},["b","21"],"And the rough",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"goat"],["i","is"],"the king of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"Grecia"],": and the great horn that",["i","is"],"between his eyes",["i","is"],"the first king."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.22","order":"02.28.008.59590"},["b","22"],"Now that being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"broken"],", whereas four stood up for it, four kingdoms shall stand up out of the nation, but not in his power."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.23","order":"02.28.008.59591"},["b","23"],"And in the latter time of their kingdom, when the transgressors are come to the full, a king of fierce countenance, and understanding",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"dark sentences"],", shall stand up."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.24","order":"02.28.008.59592"},["b","24"],"And his power shall be mighty, but not by his own power: and he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"destroy"],"wonderfully, and shall prosper, and practise, and shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"destroy"],"the mighty and the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"holy"],"people."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.25","order":"02.28.008.59593"},["b","25"],"And through his policy also he shall cause craft to prosper in his hand; and he shall magnify",["i","himself"],"in his heart, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"by peace"],"shall destroy many: he shall also stand up against the Prince of princes; but he shall be broken",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"without"],"hand."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.26","order":"02.28.008.59594"},["b","26"],"And the vision of the evening and the morning which was told",["i","is"],"true: wherefore shut thou up the vision; for it",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"shall"],"be"],"for many days."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.27","order":"02.28.008.59595"},["b","27"],"And I Daniel fainted, and was sick",["i","certain"],"days; afterward I rose up, and did the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"king’s"],"business; and I was astonished at the vision, but none understood",["i","it."]]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.2a","order":"02.28.008.59596"},["b","2a"],["span.small","HEB"],"water-course.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.16"},"Dan. 8:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/11.1.1-5"},"1 Ne. 11:1 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.3a","order":"02.28.008.59598"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.20"},"Dan. 8:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.4a","order":"02.28.008.59600"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.40"},"Dan. 11:40"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.4b","order":"02.28.008.59602"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.3"},"Dan. 11:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.5a","order":"02.28.008.59604"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.21"},"Dan. 8:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.7a","order":"02.28.008.59606"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"enraged."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.7b","order":"02.28.008.59608"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.11"},"Dan. 11:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.8a","order":"02.28.008.59610"},["b","8a"],["span.small","HEB"],"instead of it."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.8b","order":"02.28.008.59612"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.6"},"Dan. 7:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.4.3-4"},"11:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.9a","order":"02.28.008.59614"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.8"},"Dan. 7:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.10a","order":"02.28.008.59616"},["b","10a"],["span.small","OR"],"against."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.11a","order":"02.28.008.59618"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/29.38"},"Ex. 29:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.11b","order":"02.28.008.59620"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/12.11"},"Dan. 12:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.11c","order":"02.28.008.59622"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.21.20-21"},"Ezek. 7:21 (20–21)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.31"},"Dan. 11:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.13a","order":"02.28.008.59624"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/saints"},"TG Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.16a","order":"02.28.008.59626"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.2"},"Dan. 8:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.16b","order":"02.28.008.59628"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.21"},"Dan. 9:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.19.19,26"},"Luke 1:19 (19, 26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.21"},"D&C 128:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.18a","order":"02.28.008.59630"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.21"},"Dan. 9:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.19a","order":"02.28.008.59632"},["b","19a"],["span.small","IE"],"in the latter part of the period of indignation, or in the last days."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.20a","order":"02.28.008.59634"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.3"},"Dan. 8:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.21a","order":"02.28.008.59636"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.5"},"Dan. 8:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.21b","order":"02.28.008.59638"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/10.20"},"Dan. 10:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.2"},"11:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.22a","order":"02.28.008.59640"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.4"},"Dan. 11:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.23a","order":"02.28.008.59642"},["b","23a"],["span.small","HEB"],"riddles."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.24a","order":"02.28.008.59644"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.21"},"Dan. 7:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.24b","order":"02.28.008.59646"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/17.17"},"Rev. 17:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.24c","order":"02.28.008.59648"},["b","24c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.26.24-26"},"Moses 7:26 (24–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.25a","order":"02.28.008.59650"},["b","25a"],["span.small","OR"],"in a time of peace."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.25b","order":"02.28.008.59652"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.34"},"Dan. 2:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/65.2"},"D&C 65:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.26a","order":"02.28.008.59654"},["b","26a"],["span.small","IE"],"pertains to many days hereafter."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/8.27a","order":"02.28.008.59656"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/6.3"},"Dan. 6:3"],"."]]}
